overnment-dozens-block-tel-aviv-highway/0000018d-03f3-dd07-a7df-cbfbeb930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列并未正式承认亚美尼亚种族灭绝，而是用它来嘲讽土耳其埃尔多安</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-doesnt-officially-recognize-the-armenian-genocide-but-uses-it-to-taunt-erdogan/0000018d-03cd-d832-a59d-17ff395e0000</link><description>据报道，作为以色列高级政治领导层对土耳其蓄意升级的一部分，以色列外交部长在一条推文中承认“土耳其犯下了亚美尼亚种族灭绝罪”</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 18:09:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israel-doesnt-officially-recognize-the-armenian-genocide-but-uses-it-to-taunt-erdogan/0000018d-03cd-d832-a59d-17ff395e0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方下令向反内塔尼亚胡抗议组织者支付律师费</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ordered-to-pay-legal-fees-of-anti-netanyahu-protest-organizer/0000018d-03a8-dd07-a7df-cbfa13020000</link><description>在抗议者告诉人群警方正在创造侵犯民主权利的条件后，法官猛烈抨击警方逮捕了抗议者并禁止他进入抗议现场</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 16:47:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-ordered-to-pay-legal-fees-of-anti-netanyahu-protest-organizer/0000018d-03a8-dd07-a7df-cbfa13020000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人在特拉维夫举行24小时大规模集会，要求释放加沙人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/24-hour-rally-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza-set-to-take-place-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-0369-d832-a59d-17ffd4a10000</link><description>&amp;#39;世界在哪里？决策者在哪里？恳求人质的母亲 ■ 播放法国总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的视频致辞 ■ 计划周一上午在全国范围内进行 100 分钟的声援罢工</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 16:31:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/24-hour-rally-for-release-of-hostages-held-in-gaza-set-to-take-place-in-tel-aviv/0000018d-0369-d832-a59d-17ffd4a10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列妇女向正统男子提供非犹太三明治后，警方对她进行了询问</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/police-question-israeli-woman-after-she-offered-non-kosher-sandwich-to-orthodox-man/0000018d-022b-dd07-a7df-cb7b91010000</link><description>事件发生前一天，学校经理被记录与一名查巴德特使对峙，查巴德特使在学校正门前搭建了一个佩戴 Tefillin（命匣）的架子。</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 10:25:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/police-question-israeli-woman-after-she-offered-non-kosher-sandwich-to-orthodox-man/0000018d-022b-dd07-a7df-cb7b91010000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高级警官被指控性行为不端</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</link><description>这名被指控违反信任罪的警官还被勒令离开车站一周。这名妇女正在嫌疑人监管的警察局中作为志愿者完成国民服役</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 09:23:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/senior-israeli-police-officer-accused-of-sexual-misconduct/0000018d-0210-d832-a59d-16b78b180000</guid></item><item><title>“南非声称哈马斯并不存在，一切都是以色列造成的”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/two-days-of-genocide-hearings-at-the-hague-conclude-as-israel-enters-worlds-microscope/0000018c-ffef-d517-af9d-ffff79140000</link><description>尽管国际法学者赞扬以色列团队在联合国最高法院的辩护，但他们预测以色列团队将出台临时措施，可能损害以色列形象并造成政治、外交和法律伤害</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 07:42:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/two-days-of-genocide-hearings-at-the-hague-conclude-as-israel-enters-worlds-microscope/0000018c-ffef-d517-af9d-ffff79140000</guid></item><item><title>“我有土地，但我没有”：西岸橄榄收成是加沙战争的又一受害者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-have-land-but-i-dont-west-bank-olive-harvest-is-yet-another-casualty-of-gaza-war/0000018c-ff8e-dd94-a9cc-ffeeb6910000</link><description>加沙战争使约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人的生活变得困难。除了检查站和封闭的道路外，橄榄园也被宣布为禁区。上周收割结束后，三分之一的农作物仍留在树上，剥夺了巴勒斯坦人生计的一个关键要素</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 05:12:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2024-01-13/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/i-have-land-but-i-dont-west-bank-olive-harvest-is-yet-another-casualty-of-gaza-war/0000018c-ff8e-dd94-a9cc-ffeeb6910000</guid></item><item><title>卡塔尔为加沙的以色列人质提供药品，双方正在审查运送药品的人员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article-live/u-s-continues-strikes-against-houthis-in-yemen-rockets-fired-at-gaza-border-communities/0000018d-007e-dd07-a7df-cb7e2a050000</link><description>以色列公布了在加沙战斗中丧生的一名士兵的名字，三人伤势较重 ■ 以色列国防军：三名恐怖分子在约旦河西岸定居点附近的枪击事件中丧生 ■ 根据卡塔尔斡旋的协议，药品将在“未来几天”内转移到加沙的以色列人质手中更多药品进入加沙 ■ 报告：以色列和埃及之间关于以色列意图控制埃及-加沙边境地区的争端 ■ 美国袭击萨那胡塞武装目标</description><pubDate>Sat, 13 Jan 2024 03:07:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article-live/u-s-continues-strikes-against-houthis-in-yemen-rockets-fired-at-gaza-border-communities/0000018d-007e-dd07-a7df-cb7e2a050000</guid></item><item><title>以色列在约旦河西岸定居点附近发生枪击事件，以色列国防军击毙三名恐怖分子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wounded-in-shooting-near-west-bank-settlement-idf-kills-three-terrorists/0000018c-ffb1-d832-a59d-ffb7c3ee0000</link><description>周五晚上，三名枪手渗透到约旦河西岸的阿多拉定居点，通过外围围栏的缺口进入，并在与以色列国防军的交火中丧生。建议居民将自己锁在家里直到早上</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 22:22:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-13/ty-article/.premium/israeli-wounded-in-shooting-near-west-bank-settlement-idf-kills-three-terrorists/0000018c-ffb1-d832-a59d-ffb7c3ee0000</guid></item><item><title>南非犹太板球运动员在世界杯前被解除 U-19 国家队队长职务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/jewish-south-african-cricketer-removed-as-captain-of-u-19-natl-team-ahead-of-world-cup/0000018c-fe33-d832-a59d-feb773b60000</link><description>大卫·蒂格因公开支持在加沙作战的以色列士兵而被正式免职，原因是即将举行的 19 岁以下板球世界杯存在安全问题</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 19:41:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/jewish-south-african-cricketer-removed-as-captain-of-u-19-natl-team-ahead-of-world-cup/0000018c-fe33-d832-a59d-feb773b60000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡表示，药品将在“未来几天内”转移给加沙的以色列人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-medicine-will-be-transferred-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-in-the-next-few-days/0000018c-fed6-d517-af9d-fefebbf10000</link><description>卡塔尔斡旋的协议将允许向以色列人质提供处方药，而以色列将允许更多药品进入加沙</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 18:32:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-medicine-will-be-transferred-to-israeli-hostages-in-gaza-in-the-next-few-days/0000018c-fed6-d517-af9d-fefebbf10000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长和国家检察官办公室因未调查 NSO 向加纳出售 Pegasus 间谍软件而受到谴责</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-reprimanded-for-not-investigating-sale-of-pegasus-spyware-to-ghana/0000018c-fdff-d832-a59d-fdff63900000</link><description>超过 50 人组成的团体提请注意对外交部和国防部官员批准该交易的方式的怀疑</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:24:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-reprimanded-for-not-investigating-sale-of-pegasus-spyware-to-ghana/0000018c-fdff-d832-a59d-fdff63900000</guid></item><item><title>“严重扭曲”：以色列在世界法院听证会上拒绝加沙种族灭绝指控</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/profoundly-distorted-israel-rejects-gaza-genocide-accusations-in-world-court-hearing/0000018c-fdb8-dd94-a9cc-fffcda970000</link><description>以色列呼吁国际法院以毫无根据为由驳回该案，并驳回南非关于停止以色列国防军在加沙行动的请愿。以色列代表：整个案件“取决于对现实的故意策划、脱节和操纵性描述”</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 15:01:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/profoundly-distorted-israel-rejects-gaza-genocide-accusations-in-world-court-hearing/0000018c-fdb8-dd94-a9cc-fffcda970000</guid></item><item><title>在国际法院听证会上，以色列尽管政客愚笨，但仍提出强有力的辩护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</link><description>海牙的种族灭绝事件并不是由不成比例的军事反应或大量巴勒斯坦人伤亡引发的。这是以色列政治特征的直接结果：鲁莽和煽动性的冗长，而以色列总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡对此予以纵容。他甚至添加了一些自己的宝石</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:06:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/at-intl-court-of-justice-israel-presents-robust-defense-despite-half-wit-politicians/0000018c-fdaa-d517-af9d-fdbe8aee0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的“战线统一”也增强了伊朗国内代理人的地位</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</link><description>真主党、也门胡塞武装和伊拉克什叶派民兵组织已经在国内的战斗中取得了成果，而且他们并不打算在加沙战争结束后停止。</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 14:05:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-01-12/ty-article/.premium/the-unity-of-fronts-against-israel-also-enhanced-status-of-irans-proxies-domestically/0000018c-fd6e-d517-af9d-fd7e6f1a0000</guid></item><item><title>一系列失败证明以色列安全理念已经过时</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</link><description>情报一次又一次失败，现在两线作战，平民后方遭受前所未有的攻势。以色列国防军的威慑力曾有效应对 20 世纪 60 年代的威胁，但如今需要不同的解决方案。旧制度已经破产</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 13:19:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/a-series-of-failures-proves-that-israels-security-concept-is-obsolete/0000018c-fda7-d517-af9d-fdbff7850000</guid></item><item><title>五十万加沙人正在遭受严重饥饿。让其沉入其中</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</link><description>加沙危机的范围变得越来越清晰；据联合国称，以色列正在创造条件，使加沙的生活变得不可能；但以色列领导人却毫不在意</description><pubDate>Fri, 12 Jan 2024 12:29:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-01-12/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/half-a-million-gazans-are-suffering-from-acute-hunger-let-that-sink-in/0000018c-fd57-d517-af9d-fd7f19b10000</guid></item></channel></rss>